## 4 · Nested Stack — stack داخل tab

```dart
// مثال: tab الـ {feature} فيه list + detail + form
AutoRoute(
  page: HomeRoute.page,
  children: [
    AutoRoute(
      page: {Feature}ListRoute.page,
      path: '{feature}',
      children: [
        // detail داخل نفس الـ stack
        AutoRoute(path: ':id', page: {Feature}DetailRoute.page),
        AutoRoute(path: 'new', page: {Feature}FormRoute.page),
        AutoRoute(path: ':id/edit', page: {Feature}FormRoute.page),
      ],
    ),
  ],
),

// Navigation من {Feature}ListScreen — يبقى داخل نفس الـ tab stack
context.router.push({Feature}DetailRoute(id: entity.id));
```

